{"tid":587344,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚應唔應該要有自信？","createTime":"2018-03-10T10:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T11:41:36.000Z","uid":147159,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ca189f60015812c673e35820fc81dc0a4b2cb1f9","tid":587344,"uid":147159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"啱啱搭巴士聽到前面兩個男人討論緊溝女，<br />\n一肥一瘦，其中聽到兩段說話係令我有啲驚訝<br />\n<br />\n肥仔：我唔鍾意同靚女拍拖<br />\n<br />\n排骨仔：點解咁講啊你都未拍過拖<br />\n<br />\n肥仔：總之就覺得唔係好夾，唔係個外表唔夾，係性格方面，靚女多數都係雞，正臭雞<br />\n<br />\n排骨仔：姐係你覺得靚女多數貪錢？<br />\n<br />\n肥仔：錢事小啦，錢方面唔係問題，我而加成日係屋企打機，每個月份糧都有錢剩，我只係唔想佢因為鍾意我啲錢而同我一齊<br />\n<br />\n大致上係咁，真係比佢笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到自己有得揀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知你兩位有冇上連登啦，但係我想話你知，<br />\n你屋企無鏡都痾篤尿照下自己個撚樣啦大佬啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e12e85cf5697ed6b29deb7c31c3550e10e01f4f","tid":587344,"uid":45772,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺偷聽人講嘢呢個行為真係好冇品？"},{"pid":"84a238ddd26e1ca39578ab22228264c2cee385e9","tid":587344,"uid":18908,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"應該真係連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講野語氣十足十連登啲毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a93c6cf9e64f6f58db8c747cf68032708a0b73","tid":587344,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"Ching Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa